                    <div id="collapseOne" class="collapse show ps-3" aria-labelledby="headingOne"
                         data-mdb-parent="#accordionExample">
                        Welcome to The Price Prowler, where our relentless commitment is to empower you with smart savings. It all started with a spark of inspiration: What if we could simplify the process of sifting through a myriad of online seller platforms, making your shopping experience as seamless and cost-effective as possible?
                        <br /><br />
